OL,3,CAfcon final result overturned and
OL,4,CMorocco named tournament winners
OL,6,FMorocco was stunningly awarded the
OL,7,FAfrica Cup of Nations title on Tuesday
OL,8,Fby appeals judges who overturned
OL,9,FSenegal's victory in a chaotic final
OL,10,Fback in January.
OL,12,FThe Confederation of African Football
OL,13,F(CAF) said its appeal board ruled
OL,14,FSenegal is "declared to have forfeited
OL,15,Fthe final" and its 1-0 win in extra
OL,16,Ftime becomes a 3-0 default win for
OL,17,Fhost nation Morocco.
